queryData.query: select username, startTimestamp, terminationTimestamp, endTimestamp, duration, if (isActive=0 ,'False','True') as isActive, userstoreDomain, tenantDomain, remoteIp, if (rememberMeFlag=0 ,'False','True') as  rememberMeFlag, timeStamp from sessionInfoTable WHERE timeStamp >= 'begin' AND timeStamp <= 'finish'
